<li id="cite_note-stein-3"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-stein_3-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-stein_3-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-stein_3-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-stein_3-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-stein_3-4"><sup><i><b>e</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-stein_3-5"><sup><i><b>f</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-stein_3-6"><sup><i><b>g</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-stein_3-7"><sup><i><b>h</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-stein_3-8"><sup><i><b>i</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-stein_3-9"><sup><i><b>j</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-stein_3-10"><sup><i><b>k</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation web">Dorothy Stein (1997-10-27). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.hollings.mmu.ac.uk/~dtyler/ecochallenge/LAUNDRY_BALLS.htm">"Laundry Balls"</a>. Faculty of Food, Clothing and Hospitality Management at <a href="/wiki/Manchester_Metropolitan_University" title="Manchester Metropolitan University">Manchester Metropolitan University</a><span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.hollings.mmu.ac.uk/~dtyler/ecochallenge/LAUNDRY_BALLS.htm">http://www.hollings.mmu.ac.uk/~dtyler/ecochallenge/LAUNDRY_BALLS.htm</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 2010-07-09</span>.</span><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Laundry+Balls&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Dorothy+Stein&amp;rft.au=Dorothy+Stein&amp;rft.date=1997-10-27&amp;rft.pub=Faculty+of+Food%2C+Clothing+and+Hospitality+Management+at+%5B%5BManchester+Metropolitan+University%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollings.mmu.ac.uk%2F%7Edtyler%2Fecochallenge%2FLAUNDRY_BALLS.htm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Laundry_ball"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-publico-4"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-publico_4-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-publico_4-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-publico_4-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-publico_4-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-publico_4-4"><sup><i><b>e</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.publico.es/359796/sanidad-frena-el-timo-de-la-ecobola">Sanidad frena el timo de la 'ecobola'. El Instituto Nacional de Consumo requiere a 14 fabricantes que acaben con la publicidad engañosa de estos productos</a>, <a href="/wiki/P%C3%BAblico_(Spain)" title="Público (Spain)"><i>Público</i></a>, Ainhoa Iriberri, 5 February 2011, Spanish. "The Instituto Nacional del Consumo (INC) has required the manufacturers of laundry balls (...) (also called ecoballs) to cease their deceiving publicity (...) The requirement has been issued after the making (...) of a study on 14 brands of ecoballs, made to find out the most obvious: if it's true that they are effective to wash clothes. The results of the work offer no doubts: the laundry balls do clean, yes, but the same or even less than water."</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-ocu-5"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-ocu_5-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-ocu_5-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-ocu_5-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-ocu_5-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-ocu_5-4"><sup><i><b>e</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-ocu_5-5"><sup><i><b>f</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-ocu_5-6"><sup><i><b>g</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.ocu.org/equipamiento-del-hogar/ecobola-como-lavar-con-agua-s465574.htm">"Ecobola: como lavar con agua"</a> (in Spanish), <i>Compra Maestra</i> (OCU <a href="/w/index.php?title=Organizaci%C3%B3n_de_Consumidores_y_Usuarios&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Organización de Consumidores y Usuarios (page does not exist)">Organización de Consumidores y Usuarios</a>) (340), September 2009<span class="printonly">, <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.ocu.org/equipamiento-del-hogar/ecobola-como-lavar-con-agua-s465574.htm">http://www.ocu.org/equipamiento-del-hogar/ecobola-como-lavar-con-agua-s465574.htm</a></span>, "[translation] In conclusion, the results of the Ecobola are far from those obtained with detergent. We can well attribute its "washing efficacy" to the mechanical action of the washing machine and to the temperature of the washing water... with which using this product is practically the same as washing only with water. (...) The advice of the OCU: if you want to spend less money and reduce residues, choose one of the detergents recommended in our last analysis and experiment until finding the minimal dosis that gives you good results."</span><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Ecobola%3A+como+lavar+con+agua&amp;rft.jtitle=Compra+Maestra&amp;rft.date=September+2009&amp;rft.issue=340&amp;rft.pub=OCU+%5B%5BOrganizaci%C3%B3n+de+Consumidores+y+Usuarios%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ocu.org%2Fequipamiento-del-hogar%2Fecobola-como-lavar-con-agua-s465574.htm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Laundry_ball"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-mendelson-6"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-mendelson_6-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-mendelson_6-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-mendelson_6-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-mendelson_6-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-mendelson_6-4"><sup><i><b>e</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-mendelson_6-5"><sup><i><b>f</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-mendelson_6-6"><sup><i><b>g</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-mendelson_6-7"><sup><i><b>h</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-mendelson_6-8"><sup><i><b>i</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation" id="CITEREFCheryl_Mendelson2005">Cheryl Mendelson (2005), <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://books.google.com/books?id=6-gRK9HMQKoC"><i>Laundry: the home comforts book of caring for clothes and linens</i></a> (illustrated ed.), Simon and Schuster, pp.&#160;82, 83, <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0-7432-7145-9,_9780743271455" title="Special:BookSources/0-7432-7145-9, 9780743271455">0-7432-7145-9, 9780743271455</a><span class="printonly">, <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://books.google.com/books?id=6-gRK9HMQKoC">http://books.google.com/books?id=6-gRK9HMQKoC</a></span></span><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Laundry%3A+the+home+comforts+book+of+caring+for+clothes+and+linens&amp;rft.aulast=Cheryl+Mendelson&amp;rft.au=Cheryl+Mendelson&amp;rft.date=2005&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B82%2C+83&amp;rft.edition=illustrated&amp;rft.pub=Simon+and+Schuster&amp;rft.isbn=0-7432-7145-9%2C+9780743271455&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3D6-gRK9HMQKoC&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Laundry_ball"><span style="display: none;"